#### [MODIFY] [SpatialProfile.kt](file:///c:/Users/athar/Desktop/Audix/app/src/main/java/com/audixlab/audix/audio/SpatialProfile.kt)

Re-tune all 6 profiles with scientifically-calibrated values:

| Parameter | Current L3 | New L3 | Rationale |
|-----------|-----------|--------|-----------|
| primaryPinnaNotch | −4.5 dB | −3.2 dB | HRTF literature: 3–4 dB notch sufficient for externalization |
| secondaryPinnaNotch | −2.5 dB | −1.8 dB | Reduced to maintain tonal transparency |
| torsoWarmth | +1.6 dB | +1.0 dB | ISO 11904-1: 1 dB sufficient for grounding |
| airPresence | +2.0 dB | +1.2 dB | Narrowed to 3–4 kHz only (avoid vocal sibilance) |
| reverbRt60Ms | 280 ms | 220 ms | Small room RT60 = 200-300ms; shorter = tighter |
| reverbWetDry | 0.15 | 0.10 | Lower D/R ratio for transparent depth |
| virtualizerStrength | 500 | 420 | Smoother gradient: 120→220→420→620→800 |
| loudnessBoostmB | 400 | 250 | Replaced by compressor; minimal makeup gain |

New fields to add:
- `reverbPreDelayMs: Int` — Pre-delay before early reflections (10–40ms, models direct-to-reflected gap)
- `reverbDiffusion: Int` — Controls reflection density (0–1000)
- `compressorThresholdDb: Float` — Compression onset threshold
- `compressorRatio: Float` — Compression ratio (2:1 to 4:1)
- `compressorAttackMs: Float` — Attack time
- `compressorReleaseMs: Float` — Release time
- `limiterThresholdDb: Float` — Hard ceiling for zero-distortion guarantee

